{"tid":800265,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：黃雨下「玩命」活動百出　網民怒斥不負責任","createTime":"2018-08-30T17:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T03:57:57.000Z","uid":131917,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"827521c4c5f4617e6c5e101f3d012f7b6f0de593","tid":800265,"uid":131917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180830/bkn-20180830184824871-0830_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180830%2Fbkn-20180830184824871-0830_00822_001.html&d=SnJ3DapagYs6fShdi%2BcBexxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=10365aec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180830/bkn-20180830184824871-0830_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/010448_4447d33ae63493f81aa63d47cfcf6b25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F010448_4447d33ae63493f81aa63d47cfcf6b25.jpg&h=bc7c6af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暴雨下的香港變成了「香港河」，不少人出外時都要涉水而行，水浸民宅，更有馬路因山泥傾瀉和水浸而封閉。然而，有「英勇」的市民無懼風雨，在暴雨下仍到溪澗玩水，「表演瑜伽」；更有家庭服務中心帶小學生到溪澗進行活動，形容小朋友在黃雨下仍能適應和享受郊野樂趣。不少網民狠批這些人行為自私，「出事唔好害人」、「又係一班想害消防同救護嘅人」！<br />\n<br />\n昨日（29日）一行約6人的「山友」，被爆在黃雨警告下暢遊西貢猴塘溪，並在溪澗做瑜伽動作，拍下打卡照再放上網。相片由社交專頁「山野龍咁威」轉發，版主批評這些人「玩命前請為自己家人着想，而且救護員都有家人」。有眼利的網民發現其中2名山友曾在去年7月行大東山時迷路，要消防搜索11小時尋回。<br />\n<br />\n另外相中亦有一名男子右手被包紮，版主諷指「帶傷單手上陣，令人欽敬欽敬！」也有山友以湍急的溪澗作背景，在石上表演拱橋動作，險象環生。有網民直言，萬一洪水暴漲，事主想必無法及時逃生，「尋找死神的故事。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，一間位於荃灣的家庭服務中心，同樣在黃色暴雨警告下，在溪澗進行「小學生訓練活動」。活動結束後，中心在其網站上發文及活動照片，表示參與活動的小朋友無懼風雨，在黃雨下仍享受在野的樂趣，又形容「野孩子」能在任何天氣適應和享受野外。照片中可見，參與的小學生全身濕透，更有年約8歲的男孩在小瀑布下「沖身」。<br />\n<br />\n該中心回覆東網查詢時解釋，參加者只在昨日（29日）早上到位於赤徑的溪澗約半小時，又解釋在黃雨前已離開溪澗，返回營地。並指在黃雨時，所有人已在返回中心的路途中，「多謝關心我們的安全，這也是我們首要重視的一環。」<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\nAlma Chan：有起事上嚟，有冇諗過要救你哋嘅人嘅安全同感受？祝你哋平安，有事唔好累到人呀！<br />\n<br />\nSimon Kan：黃雨戶外活動，仲要帶小朋友，你們真是十分專業。 #曲<br />\n<br />\nBenny Wong；如果不幸有意外，千萬不要出動消防救護去救他們。"},{"pid":"2aaeb31e9bd26dbf4f9634c28ed1ce159a6f1173","tid":800265,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"真係希望當時有洪水侵襲"},{"pid":"d91121b661c7379eba43e135e83c9c6646301c1c","tid":800265,"uid":14918,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"天文台無掛紅雨 即係話仲係安全啦"},{"pid":"86c639377c8dc4bf3da525043c883dd177de91a3","tid":800265,"uid":810,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<br />\n黃雨又唔係話好大雨"},{"pid":"ae5dfa80bea8ef029df73f186b3e2410d9c02952","tid":800265,"uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都落過大雨都敢帶細佬去山澗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a3c32ed924c6ef31b01e9bd5eff395b02d2c5b","tid":800265,"uid":40250,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢幾日都落過大雨都敢帶細佬去山澗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係痴撚線<br />\n我夠膽講香港既山落起雨黎係好撚危險<br />\n<br />\n外國d高海拔既山就算天氣點差，都無咁危險"},{"pid":"0d492733ac5fb5c949d60980f9bcaac8c0a15349","tid":800265,"uid":146243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"新娘潭嘅故仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae948160f7da3e8e205dbca2ca993d883783811","tid":800265,"uid":1372,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"危險？問過大交合未？黃雨咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5402d936e271e6134454a42156e10ce88691d1b1","tid":800265,"uid":187076,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/013117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F013117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f06a50cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d5a9f0bffd3ba6e3c57236093db63c22e25cc10","tid":800265,"uid":160502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:46:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃雨</span></span><br />\n大交合：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216a708c798d743ac2842e366ca01d2b76f4f460","tid":800265,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17370e6216cb0e7261d314947d63efeaaa70c4e0","tid":800265,"uid":106341,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T18:00:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾天文台唔駛負責？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8377fe667b06d79144fb470e122b8aab73ee0c88","tid":800265,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T23:48:10.000Z","msg":"黃雨都唔駛停工，停課，小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56404e7b3069db585ec32a8fd9d6098a7b7a2e9d","tid":800265,"uid":5006,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"「黃」色信號提醒市民將有大雨並可能進一步發展至「紅」色或「黑」色暴雨情況。一些低窪地帶及排水情況欠佳的地區會出現水淹。有關政府部門、主要公共交通機構和公用事業公司應作出戒備。<br />\n<br />\n咁外出活動無問題wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學又未停課，行山又唔係低窪<br />\n要屌就屌大交合啦，屌家庭中心把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7bd717c19d6f824acc1a42e246c4